íŸ@d1caae258b9bdfc5a5aa82123c8ea53476f7fd6a937a5d7c789fce9e36e31cc9⁄=Title: title: into glob
Path: Examples
Content:
Convert string to glob.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1234' | into glob
1234

```
Convert glob to glob.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1234' | into glob | into glob
1234

```
Convert filepath to glob.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ls Cargo.toml | get name | into glob


```
